<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Sagewood</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The real estate in Sagewood comprises of single story condos, multi-story townhouses, semi-finished bungalows and empty plots of land. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Many of the listed properties have walkout basements, parking spaces and large front and back yards. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The homes available for sale in this neighborhood are ideal for both unmarried people and large families with children. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Some of the buildings come fully furnished. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The buildings here are inspired by Prairie, Colonial Ranch and Heritage-inspired classic architecture.</p>
        </div>
